<paragraph id="49055A52755C8129FF71CC65FD08FD32" blockId="12.[151,1436,596,683]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">A speciebus omnibus generis Sphyrospermi combinatione characterum: foliis exiguis ellipticis, marginibus pallide coloratis crassisque, pedicellis corollisque elongatis, calyce corollaque brevi-pilosis, filamentis ubique quoad longitudinem antherae comparate brevibus differt.</paragraph>
